# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.1] 2022-03-16
### Fixed
 - Authorized keys was always set for the {{ ansuble_user }} and not for the {{ sysadmin_user }}

## [1.0.0] 2022-03-16
### Added
 - Create a sysadmin user
 - Copy public authorized keys
 - Add as sudoer
 - Tests (molecule)
 - Documentation
 - Initial files
 - Add option to toggle sudoer
 - Add option to copy files for users. sysadmin_file: [{path: '', destination_path: ''}].
 - Run test in pipeline for multiple os using variable `MOLECULE_DISTRO`